

<h3 style="color:#4fc3f7; margin-bottom: 4px;">Previous large update (V10.0) - THE BIGGEST UPDATE YET</h3>
  <h3>New Features</h3>
  <h3>New Features / Reworks</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Evolution Hard Cap:</strong> You can now have a maximum of <strong>25 evolutions</strong>! (To be increased to <strong>50</strong> in a future update!)</li>
  <li><strong>Free Evolutions:</strong> Evolutions no longer cost anything — but you must now <strong>complete a challenge</strong> before each one! This also means you can sometimes evolve <strong>multiple times in a row</strong> if you’re fast enough.</li>
  <li><strong>Dynamic Requirements:</strong> Evolution goals now display how far you’ve progressed, not just the final requirement.</li>
  <li><strong>Evolver Spec Rework:</strong> Evolver spec can <strong>no longer skip</strong> evolution requirements. However, their <strong>evo loss percentages are much improved</strong> as compensation.</li>
  <li><strong>New Easter Egg:</strong> A secret has been added… <em>can you find it?</em></li>
  <li><strong>Endgoal Update:</strong> The final goal is now <strong>50 million Points</strong> (was 10 million) — but it’s now based on <strong>all-time Points</strong> instead of current Points.</li>
  <li><strong>MEGA Upgrades:</strong> Every 10th clicker upgrade now results in a MEGA upgrade — granting <strong>5×</strong> the clicking power of a normal upgrade.</li>
  <li><strong>Secret V0.1 Mode:</strong> A hidden button in the UI brings you back to the original version of the game (V0.1). All code is faithfully copied; only a warning and return button are added. Good luck finding it!</li>
</ul>

<h3>Balance Changes</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>EvoLoss Update:</strong> Losing an evolution now <strong>always resets</strong> Power and AutoPower — even if it previously didn’t.</li>
  <li><strong>Clicker Spec Buff:</strong> Clicker spec now starts every evolution with <strong>10 free Clicking Power upgrades</strong> (up from 1).</li>
  <li><strong>Offliner Spec Buff:</strong> Offliner spec now starts every evolution with <strong>10 free AutoPower upgrades</strong> (up from 0).</li>
  <li><strong>Offline Nerf:</strong> The offline multiplier now starts at <strong>10%</strong> instead of 25%, reducing the maximum possible bonus.</li>
  <li><strong>Hard Cap:</strong> You can now only evolve up to <strong>evolution 25</strong> — for now.</li>
  <li><strong>RP → Points Trade:</strong> RankPoints now convert to Points at a <strong>1% rate</strong>, but with <strong>no upper limit</strong>.</li>
  <li><strong>Mystery Gift Change:</strong> The <strong>Free Evolution</strong> reward has been replaced with a <strong>2× Points</strong> reward.</li>
  <li><strong>Rebalanced Evo Requirements:</strong> Most old requirements are now <strong>more difficult</strong>, and several new ones were added.</li>
  <li><strong>Evolution Rewards Updated:</strong> Several rewards tied to evolutions have been <strong>rebalanced or improved</strong>.</li>
  <li><strong>Spec Rewards Improved:</strong> Specialization benefits have been <strong>buffed overall</strong>.</li>
  <li><strong>Rank Rewards Tweaked:</strong> Rank bonuses have been <strong>rearranged and rebalanced</strong>.</li>
</ul>

<h3>UI/UX – Quality of Life – Tweaks</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Coin Display:</strong> You can now see your <strong>current Coins</strong> directly inside the Coin Shop!</li>
  <li><strong>Stat Panel:</strong> The <strong>Stats</strong> page has been visually updated for clarity.</li>
  <li><strong>PermaPower Tooltip:</strong> PermaPower now includes an <strong>info box</strong> explaining its effect.</li>
  <li><strong>Small UI Tweaks:</strong> Various minor adjustments to layout and visuals (especially on <strong>desktop</strong>).</li>
  <li><strong>Updated Endgoal Message:</strong> The message shown after reaching the endgoal has been improved.</li>
  <li><strong>Spec Explanations:</strong> Specializations now provide <strong>clearer descriptions</strong> of what they do.</li>
  <li><strong>Locked Buttons Hidden:</strong> Buttons for content you haven’t unlocked are now <strong>hidden</strong> instead of greyed out.</li>
  <li><strong>New Circle Color:</strong> The main click-circle now better matches the overall <strong>aesthetic</strong> of the game.</li>
  <li><strong>Offliner Rank Shop Access:</strong> The Offliner spec can now enter the Rank Shop at Evolution 3. However, all non-automatic upgrades remain locked until Evolution 8.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Bug & Issue Fixes</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Mobile Click Bug Fixed:</strong> Tapping the Circle no longer shifts the layout on <strong>mobile devices</strong>.</li>
  <li><strong>Color Reset Fix:</strong> Color themes now update <strong>immediately</strong> after a reset.</li>
  <li><strong>Click Sound Fix:</strong> Fixed a bug where <strong>clicking too fast</strong> caused audio issues.</li>
</ul>

